 Fireboy DML Fireboy DML’s ‘Peru is still paraing’ as the singer is set to release a new project Peru Airlines, featuring international acts 21 Savage and Blxst.   The singer’s management outfit Empire announced the project release in a tweet on Wednesday that has received over 14.8k likes. The project is expected to drop on Friday, February 11, 2022. FIREBOY DML
